      <title>sonoff snzb-04 zigbee aperture controller</title>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;The SONOFF SNZB-04 Wireless Door/Window Sensor is essential for knowing who is entering and leaving your home, so it is most often used as part of a smart security system. As a home assistant, it is also zigbee2mqtt compatible and integrates the latest version of the zigbee 3.0 protocol.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
